Installation Instructions
Jan. 27, 2013

1. Move/copy the .svg icon into /usr/share/icons/hicolor/scalable/actions
$ sudo cp purse-thief.svg /usr/share/icons/hicolor/scalable/actions

2. Regenerate the GTK icon cahce by running:
$ sudo gtk-update-icon-cache /usr/share/icons/hicolor/

3. Install mpg321 (or globally substitute your preferred CLI mp3 player in alarm.py, if it responds to -q for quiet and -g for gain.)
$sudo apt-get install mpg321

4. Ensure you have the tp_smapi module installed and loaded.

5.. Now start the applet, or add this to be run on startup:
$ python alarm.py